{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7c8d28bdad","title":"七律·有所思","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ceb4ea206","index":0,"year":1966,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"7c8d28bdad"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"7c74345a4e","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"7c8d28bdad","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"神都，古谓京城。这里指首都北京。"},{"id":"378577450e","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"7c8d28bdad","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"南国，中国南方的泛称。作者写这首诗的时候，正在南方巡视。1966年5月15日至6月15日在杭州：途经长沙于17日到韶山滴水洞，在这里住了11天；28日赴武汉。"},{"id":"ed9fb3042a","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"7c8d28bdad","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"凭闲静听蒲满雨，化用岳飞《满江红·怒发冲冠》词“凭闲处满满雨歇”句。开同栏。满满，骤急的雨势。"},{"id":"aefc1a932d","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"7c8d28bdad","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"故国，即祖国。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e8c516dc01","type":"title","text":"七律·有所思","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"7c8d28bdad"},{"id":"7c74345a4e","type":"paragraph","text":"正是神都有事时，又来南国踏芳枝。青松怒向苍天发，败叶纷随碧水驰。一阵风雷惊世界，满街红绿走旋旗。凭闲静听满满雨，故国M人民有所思。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"7c8d28bdad"}],"page":{"id":"914f9a1859","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"7c8d28bdad","start":392,"end":392}}}},"__N_SSG":true}